<%= content_for :page_css do %>
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag "default" %>
<% end %>

<body>

  <div class = "white">    
    <p>In this experiment, you will be using your mouse to control a robot
    and search a water tank.</p>

    <p>The risks and discomfort associated with participation in this study
    are no greater than those ordinarily encountered in daily life.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="colored">
    <h3>Standard Adult Consent Form</h3>

    <p>This consent form has been designed for individuals who are
    least 18 years old. If you are not 18 years old or older, please
    do not participate in this experiment.</p>

    <p>This study has been approved by Princeton University's Institutional
    Review Panel for Human Subjects. I hereby give my consent to participate
    in your research. You have given me:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>An explanation of the procedures to be followed in the project.</li>
      </ul>
    <p>I understand that:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>My participation is voluntary, and I may withdraw my consent
        and discontinue participation in the project at any time. My refusal
        to participate will not result in any penalty.</li>
	<li>By signing this agreement, I <i><b>do not waive</b></i> any
        legal rights or release Princeton University, its agents, or you
        from liability for negligence.</li>
      </ul>
	
      <form method="post">
        <input type="hidden" name="state" value="instructions" />
	<input type='hidden' name='auth_code' value='<%= auth_code %>' />
	<input type="hidden" name="subject" value="<%= subject %>" />
	<input type="submit" name="consent" value="Yes, I consent. Let's start the survey." />
      </form>
  </div>

</body>
